
Code for submission: Uncovering Currency Bias and Syntax Gap in Text Embedding Models

Notebooks :

  MRR.ipynb – Evaluates syntactic sensitivity gaps introduced by currency substitution
  
  associative_bias.ipynb – Analyzes associative (digital classism) bias between currencies and concepts such as luxury, poverty, malice, and lawfulness
  
  sentiment_analysis.ipynb – Studies sentiment shifts caused by replacing currency tokens in otherwise identical texts
  
  sts.ipynb – Measures the effect of currency token replacements on semantic textual similarity scores.


